TITLE: Installing Plugin Dependencies with Bundler (Shell)
DESCRIPTION: Shell command using Bundler (`bundle install`) to install the Ruby gem dependencies defined in the plugin's `Gemfile`. This command should be run within the plugin's root directory after cloning the repository.
