TITLE: Log4j2 Log File Rollover and Strategy Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Configures log file rotation with policies based on time and size, including max file count and file retention rules. Defines how log files are renamed, retained, or deleted during rollover events, with detailed parameters for policies, strategy, and conditions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/logstash/blob/main/docs/reference/logging.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
appender.rolling.type = RollingFile
appender.rolling.name = plain_rolling
appender.rolling.fileName = ${sys:ls.logs}/logstash-plain.log
appender.rolling.filePattern = ${sys:ls.logs}/logstash-plain-%d{yyyy-MM-dd}-%i.log.gz
appender.rolling.policies.type = Policies
appender.rolling.policies.time.type = TimeBasedTriggeringPolicy
appender.rolling.policies.time.interval = 1
appender.rolling.policies.time.modulate = true
appender.rolling.layout.type = PatternLayout
appender.rolling.layout.pattern = [%d{ISO8601}][%-5p][%-25c]%notEmpty{[%X{pipeline.id}]}%notEmpty{[%X{plugin.id}]} %m%n
appender.rolling.policies.size.type = SizeBasedTriggeringPolicy
appender.rolling.policies.size.size = 100MB
appender.rolling.strategy.type = DefaultRolloverStrategy
appender.rolling.strategy.max = 30
appender.rolling.strategy.action.type = Delete
appender.rolling.strategy.action.basepath = ${sys:ls.logs}
appender.rolling.strategy.action.condition.type = IfFileName
appender.rolling.strategy.action.condition.glob = logstash-plain-*
appender.rolling.strategy.action.condition.nested_condition.type = IfLastModified
appender.rolling.strategy.action.condition.nested_condition.age = 7D
```

