TITLE: Remove macOS Quarantine Attribute - Specific Directory
DESCRIPTION: This command removes the quarantine attribute specifically from the `logstash-{{version}}` directory on macOS.  It is used to address Gatekeeper issues. This example assumes `logstash-{{version}}` is the extracted Logstash directory. It requires the `xattr` command-line tool.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/logstash/blob/main/docs/reference/first-event.md#_snippet_3

