TITLE: Creating Logstash CPM User API Key in Elasticsearch
DESCRIPTION: Creates an API key for a Central Pipeline Management (CPM) user with permissions to manage Logstash pipelines and monitor the cluster. The key expires after 365 days.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/logstash/blob/main/ci/serverless/README.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
POST /_security/api_key
{
  "name": "cpm_user",
  "expiration": "365d",   
  "role_descriptors": { 
    "cpm_user_role": {
      "cluster": ["manage_logstash_pipelines", "monitor"]
    }
  }
}
```

